{"tid":2226299,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美版香港難民法: 將聯同英國等國建立簽證篩選機制","createTime":"2020-10-02T03:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T03:26:44.000Z","uid":305299,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4cb51f1dc67f2991ca8b5d0109d4b7b828586f","tid":2226299,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6mcLru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6mcLru.png&h=c74ab4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來尋晚啱啱通過眾議院委員會嘅《香港人民自由和選擇法案》入面包含咗條文，講明要聯合英國及並他國家，一齊聯手篩走腐敗官員及有問題人士嘅移民申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大家就唔使擔心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以睇睇 google translate 翻譯出來嘅第8(b)(3) 條同第8(b)(4) 條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>國務卿應與其他聯邦機構的負責人協商，制定一項計劃，與包括聯合王國在內的其他國家進行合作，以期達到以下目的：<br />\n   &hellip;&hellip;..<br />\n<br />\n（3）查明並防止腐敗官員利用移民和簽證政策及程序；和<br />\n<br />\n（4）根據以下情況，加快共享與拒絕香港特別行政區居民個人簽證或其他旅行證件的個人申請有關的信息：<br />\n（A）&hellip;.. 國家安全或相關理由；或（B）&hellip;. 欺詐或虛假陳述。<br />\n<br />\nThe Secretary of State, in consultation with the heads of other Federal agencies, as appropriate, shall develop a plan to engage with other nations, including the United Kingdom, on cooperative efforts to&mdash; <br />\n   &hellip;&hellip;..<br />\n<br />\n(3) identify and prevent the exploitation of immigration and visa policies and procedures by corrupt officials; and<br />\n<br />\n(4) expedite the sharing of information, as appropriate, related to the refusal of individual applications for visas or other travel documents submitted by residents of the Hong Kong SAR based on&mdash;<br />\n(A) national security or related grounds under section 212(a)(3) of the Immigration and Nationality Act (8 U.S.C. 1182(a)(3)); or (B) fraud or misrepresentation under section 212(a)(6)(C) of the Immigration and Nationality Act (8 U.S.C. 1182(a)(6)(C)).</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然法案仲要再排期上大會同參議院，但大家可以去草案發起人新澤西州民主黨國會眾議員 Tom Malinowski 個 twitter 畀心心:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repmalinowski\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepmalinowski&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAqF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=c62942f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repmalinowski</a><br />\n<br />\n《香港人民自由和選擇法案》初稿:<br />\n<a href=\"https://malinowski.house.gov/sites/malinowski.house.gov/files/Hong%20Kong%202020%20MALINJ_099%20-%20Malinowski%20-%20bill.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmalinowski.house.gov%2Fsites%2Fmalinowski.house.gov%2Ffiles%2FHong%2520Kong%25202020%2520MALINJ_099%2520-%2520Malinowski%2520-%2520bill.pdf&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAqF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=f5e824f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://malinowski.house.gov/sites/malinowski.house.gov/files/Hong%20Kong%202020%20MALINJ_099%20-%20Malinowski%20-%20bill.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nTom Malinowski 新聞稿:<br />\n<a href=\"https://malinowski.house.gov/media/press-releases/representative-malinowski-s-bipartisan-legislation-protect-people-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmalinowski.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Frepresentative-malinowski-s-bipartisan-legislation-protect-people-hong-kong&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAqF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=8ccb9706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://malinowski.house.gov/media/press-releases/representative-malinowski-s-bipartisan-legislation-protect-people-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"93db320875d9c27be3566491ba13c1dd4991dd66","tid":2226299,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2274056e0c18be7ba544652df5f820f2505aa8","tid":2226299,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca4e674d0629ac89d4168f39f8d604053088299","tid":2226299,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4146fef03c4427ae045c2acccddf419106e12e59","tid":2226299,"uid":104425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:24:24.000Z","msg":"代賤種三毛回覆：屌你班移民撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：情況太惡劣唔敢講唔會移民，但未需要走之前都會抗爭到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2ab13bf00d6dc39ae92f954d1d31c1ab0c2671","tid":2226299,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"唔走就真係傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家香港人邊個唔移民<br />\n香港呢個朵已經係國際過街老鼠"}]}